HEADWORD: Tormenter
<hw>Tor*ment"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who, or that which, torments; a tormentor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An executioner.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
